VRDN-1100 is a humanized monoclonal antibody targeting IGF-1R with an equilibrium dissociation constant KD of 1.8 nM.

The lower panel of FIG. 5B illustrates a binding dose response curve, which demonstrated VRDN-1100 having an EC50=0.4 nM.
VRDN-1100 potently inhibits IGF-1 stimulated receptor phosphorylation on A549 cells (IC50=0.09 nM) and HOCF cells (IC50=0.09 nM), which is illustrated in FIG. 6A and FIG. 6B.
